  <T n="trait_description">0xF8563683<!--{0.SimFirstName}'s soul burns bright!\n\nAs a ghost, {0.SimFirstName} receives extra benefits to {0.SimPronounPossessiveDependent} Ghost Mastery stamina, enabling {0.SimPronounObjective} to perform abilities more frequently.\n\nThe Burning Soul trait persists beyond death, accompanying {0.SimFirstName} into {0.SimPronounPossessiveDependent} next life after Rebirth. {0.SimFirstName} can retain one personality trait from {0.SimPronounPossessiveDependent} previous life with the <b>Recall Past Life</b> self-interaction, along with certain other traits by using the <b>Peer Into Soul</b> interaction available on mirrors.\n\nIf {0.SimFirstName} is reborn as a younger Sim, certain developmental skills will be immediately unlocked. As an added bonus, young adults and older get the extraordinary ability to defy the boundaries of life and death, enabling <b>Transcendent WooHoo</b> as a living Sim.\n\nThis trait is a one-time blessing, accompanying {0.SimFirstName} into {0.SimPronounPossessiveDependent} next life only once.--></T>
